#: ../../source/skills/index.rst:11
msgid ""
"MaxFrame Coding Skill is an AI coding assistant released by Alibaba Cloud"
" MaxFrame. It integrates with mainstream AI coding assistants as an "
"intelligent plugin and injects MaxFrame's distributed data processing "
"knowledge into AI agents, enabling them to generate runnable MaxFrame "
"code from natural language requirements."
msgstr ""
"MaxFrame Coding Skill 是阿里云 MaxFrame 推出的 AI 编程辅助工具。它以智能"
"插件的形式集成到主流 AI 编程助手中，将 MaxFrame 完整的分布式数据处理知识"
"体系注入 AI Agent，使其能够根据自然语言描述，自动生成可直接运行的 "
"MaxFrame 代码。"

#: ../../source/skills/index.rst:17
msgid ""
"MaxFrame Coding Skill covers the full MaxFrame development workflow, from"
" session management, data reading and writing, and operator selection to "
"result writing. It lowers the entry barrier for distributed data "
"processing and improves coding efficiency."
msgstr ""
"MaxFrame Coding Skill 覆盖 MaxFrame 开发的全链路流程：从会话管理、数据"
"读写、算子选择到结果写入，降低分布式数据处理的开发门槛，提升编码效率。"

