#: ../../source/skills/index.rst:141
msgid ""
"MaxFrame provides a multi-layer operator system, including standard "
"pandas-compatible operators, MaxFrame-specific ``.mf`` extension "
"operators such as ``apply_chunk``, ``map_reduce``, ``flatmap``, and "
"``rebalance``, and UDF / UDTF capabilities. For a specific data "
"processing requirement, the Operator Selector agent built into Coding "
"Skill automatically completes operator selection and validation:"
msgstr ""
"MaxFrame 提供多层次算子体系，包括标准 pandas 兼容算子、MaxFrame 专属的 ``"
".mf`` 扩展算子（如 ``apply_chunk``、``map_reduce``、``flatmap``、``"
"rebalance`` 等），以及 UDF / UDTF 能力。面对具体的数据处理需求，Coding "
"Skill 内置的 Operator Selector 智能代理能够自动完成算子选择与验证："

#: ../../source/skills/index.rst:148
msgid ""
"**Task-driven recommendation**: recommends the best operator combination "
"based on the task description and explains the reason."
msgstr "**任务驱动推荐**：根据任务描述，自动推荐最优算子组合，并给出选择理由。"

#: ../../source/skills/index.rst:149
msgid ""
"**API authenticity validation**: validates operators against 900+ pages "
"of API documentation to prevent hallucinated APIs."
msgstr ""
"**API 真实性校验**：基于 900+ 页 API 文档实时验证算子是否存在，杜绝幻觉 "
"API。"

#: ../../source/skills/index.rst:150
msgid ""
"**Fallback alternatives**: provides alternatives, including UDF fallback "
"options, when the preferred operator has constraints."
msgstr ""
"**备选方案提供**：当首选算子存在限制时，自动提供替代方案，包括 UDF 回退"
"方案。"

